#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The health check uses OIDC endpoint discovery to validate the connection.\n"
"Therefore, discovery must be enabled."
msgstr ""
"A verificação de saúde usa a descoberta de endpoint OIDC para validar a conexão.\n"
"Portanto, a descoberta deve estar habilitada."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
